  abstract  = {There is considerable concern over declines in insect pollinator communities and potential impacts on the pollination of crops and wildflowers1-4. Among the multiple pressures facing pollinators2-4, decreasing floral resources due to habitat loss and degradation has been suggested as a key contributing factor2-8. However, a lack of
