  title     = {Impact of Currently Used or Potentially Useful Insecticides for Canola Agroecosystems on \emph{Bombus impatiens} ({Hymenoptera: Apidae}), Megachile rotundata (Hymentoptera: Megachilidae), and Osmia lignaria (Hymenoptera: Megachilidae)},
